cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the optimization of deep sum-product networks. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as deep learning is a subfield of AI. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. The paper's focus on image and text data could also place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) respectively.
